(Groupe Cantrex Inc) said it plans tomerge a new wholly-owned subsidiary a merger agreement with(CAP Appliance Purchasers Inc), of Woodstock, Ontario, a groupof about 400 appliance and electronics retailers.    It said CAP shareholders will receive 140,700 firstpreferred Groupe Cantrex shares entitling the holders toreceive 6.05 dlrs per share or the equivilant in class Asubordinate voting Cantrex shares.    The merger is effective April one and is subject toshareholder approval.          Reuter&#3;